        "Title": "A Killer View",
        "Description": "\u201cMay I remind you that this operation is to be conducted discreetly. You can\u2019t just blow everything to high heavens. The cover-up costs far exceeded what the client paid us!\u201d\r\r\u201cIt was a killer view, though, sir.\u201d\r\r\u201cOh, for God\u2019s sake, 47 - grow up.\u201d\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Fenixsandr.",
